# unpatchable by a version bump today. Where a base runs `apt-get upgrade`/`apk
# upgrade` they clear once the distro ships a fix; the minimal alpine/scratch
# finals clear on the next base rebuild. Delete each line once a fix exists.
# One CVE id per line.
